overview: The album is described in a press release as "a fantastic blend of brand-new songs, special versions and mixes of popular Delain tracks, covers, and the single 'Are You Done With Me'.  Tracks:  Invidia, Electricity,  We Are the Others, Milk and Honey, Not Enough, "Backstage Footage", Get the Devil Out of Me,  We Are the Others,  April Rain,  Frozen.
title: Delain - Interlude
